=99 (compiles libphobos with
<samp>-frelease</samp>), =E2=80=98<samp>all</samp>=E2=80=99 (same as =E2=80=
=98<samp>yes</samp>=E2=80=99), =E2=80=98<samp>none</samp>=E2=80=99 or
=E2=80=98<samp>release</samp>=E2=80=99 (same as =E2=80=98<samp>no</samp>=E2=
=80=99).
</p>
<p>Individual checks available in <var>list</var> are =E2=80=98<samp>assert=
</samp>=E2=80=99 (compiles libphobos
